 Since triangle $ACD$ is right, $\angle CAD = 90^\circ - \angle ACD = 90^\circ - 50^\circ = 40^\circ$. [asy] unitsize(2 cm); pair A, B, C, D, E, O; A = dir(90); B = dir(90 + 100); C = dir(90 - 140); D = (A + reflect(B,C)*(A))/2;
